---
// Features.astro - Black background features section
---

<section class="py-24 bg-black text-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-16 text-white">Key Features</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-zinc-900 rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 h-full flex flex-col border border-zinc-800 hover:translate-y-[-4px] transition-transform duration-300 hover:shadow-xl">
        <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Sound Reminders</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-300">Gentle, non-intrusive sounds pull you out of deep focus, ensuring smooth transitions between work and breaks. They're designed to be noticeable without being jarring.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900 rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 h-full flex flex-col border border-zinc-800 hover:translate-y-[-4px] transition-transform duration-300 hover:shadow-xl">
        <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Visual Cues</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-300">Subtle screen flashes mark session boundaries, keeping you on track without breaking your flow. The visual indicators complement the audio cues for enhanced awareness.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900 rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 h-full flex flex-col border border-zinc-800 hover:translate-y-[-4px] transition-transform duration-300 hover:shadow-xl">
        <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Do Not Disturb Integration</h4>
        <p class="text-gray-300">Leverage Mac's Do Not Disturb to block distractions while allowing critical notifications. Stay in your flow state longer with fewer interruptions.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 
